rows.label: qst003205_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm glad you're safe
too, Bonono-kun, mo.

rows.label: qst003205_msg0003
rows.name: Thank you all so much, mo.

rows.label: qst003205_msg0004
rows.name: Skilled Drivers are so reliable, mo.

rows.label: qst003205_msg0005
rows.name:
Are you asking about
this Blade-san, mo?

rows.label: qst003205_msg0006
rows.name:
I met this Blade-san right after I
was separated from Bonono-kun, mo.

rows.label: qst003205_msg0007
rows.name:
While I was running away, a Core
Crystal fell from the sky, mo.

rows.label: qst003205_msg0008
rows.name:
I thought it would make a nice
present for a friend if I survived,
so when I picked it up...

rows.label: qst003205_msg0009
rows.name: I accidentally resonated with it, mo.

rows.label: qst003205_msg0010
rows.name:
Then this Blade-san was
born and protected me, mo.

rows.label: qst003205_msg0013
rows.name:
Anyway, it's dangerous
here, mo. We should evacuate
somewhere safe, mo.

rows.label: qst003205_msg0014
rows.name:
Aki-kun was worried and sent
Drivers to find us, mo?

rows.label: qst003205_msg0015
rows.name:
You can really count
on your friends, mo!

rows.label: qst003205_msg0016
rows.name:
Then let's return to Aki-kun at
Port Ananyam in Superbia, mo!

rows.label: qst003205_msg0017
rows.name: Alulu-chan should come with us, mo!
